<div class='p-3' style='max-width: 500px'>
    <form action='/signup' method='POST'>
        <div class='form-group mb-2'>
            <label for='idInputbox'>ID</label>
            <input type='text' name='id' maxlength=255 class='form-control' id='idInputbox'placeholder='Enter ID' required minlength='3' maxlength='255', onkeyup='idCheck()'>
            <p>
                <small id='goodid' class='text-success fw-bold' style='display: none'>Good ID.</small>
                <small id='badid' class='text-danger fw-bold' style='display: none'>IDs can only contain alphanumeric characters or underscores(_).</small>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class='form-group mb-2'>
            <label for='passwordInputbox'>Password</label>
            <input type='password' name='password' class='form-control' id='passwordInputbox' placeholder='Enter Password' required minlength='8' maxlength='255' onkeyup='pwMatchCheck();pwAppropriateCheck()'
            pattern='^[A-Za-z\d$@$!%*?&^#_\-+=<>,./|]{8,255}$'>
            <small class='form-text text-muted'>Passwords must be at least eight characters long.</small>
            <small id='passwordbadlength' class='text-danger fw-bold' style='display: none'>Passwords should be 8 characters or longer, 255 characters or shorter.</small>
            <small id='passwordbadchar' class='text-danger fw-bold' style='display: none'>Your password contains illegal characters: <small id='passwordbadcharlist'></small></small>
        </div>
        <div class='form-group mb-2'>
            <label for='passwordConfirmInputbox'>Confirm Password</label>
            <input type='password' name='passwordConfirm' class='form-control' id='passwordConfirmInputbox' area-describedby='passwordConfirmDesc' placeholder='Re-enter password' required minlength='9' maxlength='255' onkeyup='pwMatchCheck()'>
            <p>
                <small id='passwordmatch' class='text-success fw-bold' style='display: none'>Passwords match.</small>
                <small id='passwordnotmatch' class='text-danger fw-bold' style='display: none'>Passwords do not match.</small>
            </p>
            <small id='passwordConfirmDesc' class='form-text text-muted'>In order to ensure that you have entered your password correctly, please type it one more time.</small>
        </div>
        <p><span class='text-danger fw-bold'>WARNING!</span>    YOU CANNOT reset your password once you forget it. Make sure you make your password memorable.</p>
        <div class='mt-2 mb-2'>
            <%- captcha %>
            <div class='row'>
                <label for='captchaIn' class='col-form-label col-sm-4'>CAPTCHA</b></label>
                <div class='col-sm-8'>
                    <input class="form-control" maxlength=5 id='captchaIn' name='captcha' type="text" style='width:100px' autocomplete='off'>
                </div>
            </div>
            <small class='form-text text-muted'>For spam protection, please type <b>four</b> characters shown above.</small>
        </div>
        <p>계정을 만들면 <a href='/w/GECWiki:개인정보처리방침'>개인정보처리방침</a>에 동의하는 것입니다.</p>
        <button type='submit' class='btn btn-primary'>Sign up</button>
    </form>
    <script src='/js/signupPasswordCheck.js'></script>
</div>